**Table of Contents**

- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [License](#license)

## Installation

```console
pip install haystack-text2speech
```

## Installation

Step 1. Install the audio system dependencies. On Debian-based systems:

```console
sudo apt-get install libsndfile1 ffmpeg
```

Step 2. Install the package. With pip:

```console
pip install haystack-text2speech
```

